    "For the survey data, we adopted the constant comparative method [50] as our primary tool for category derivation.",
    "We initiated our analysis with a subset of the data to determine initial categorization.",
    "Subsequently, the remaining data portions were reviewed to verify the categorization's overarching applicability.",
    "Category modifications were made as and when emergent categories were identified.",
    "This iterative process continued until the entirety of participants' survey results were aptly analyzed using the formulated categories."
